### Welcome to GDA study home.
This website is created in July, 2020 for leaving a record track of studying while going through the textbook for bioinformatics, "Genomic Data Analysis", written by Professor Kim, Ju Han of SNU.


### Authors and Contributors
You can view the repo to this website at my profile (@seunghooh5).
